						<summary>

						<p>This inscription is incomplete. It records a gift of 14(1/2) <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Śri Pōndai-perumānaḍigaḷ by certain Mahādēva bhaṭṭaṉ, son of Maṇisivabhaṭṭa Sarvakratukkaḷ of Kūḍal, one of the members of <hi rend="italic">āḷuṅgaṇam</hi> of Rajamallach-chaturvēdimaṅgalam in Tiruvēgambapuram, a village in Dāmark-kōṭṭam.</p>						

						</summary>
